name: en-osm_viewer_v2_sw-alaska
title: World Maps & Satellite Photos
description:
Search for cities/towns with more than 1000 people. There are about 127,654 worldwide:

  • Worldwide maps with satellite photos: 11 levels of zoom with 305-meter resolution
  • North America maps: 15 levels of zoom + 4 levels of overzoom to highlight building details and natural geography
  • Satellite photos of SW Alaska: 19-meter resolution
extra_description: Thank you to the OpenStreetMap community, which makes it possible for anybody to improve these maps for the benefit of all.
